i pull 4 spiroc, round them up, if there are more than 4, partner root it. pull them to open space near ogre, snare, if resist, resnare. CoF until i am about 2 mana, run out of aggro range, med.  other wizard take over, and finish off.<br>
<br>
important part here is 2 wiz should not try to alt nuke, if pull split, it will make thing harder.<br>
